<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>婚礼只剩下几天了，婚纱也已经做好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人忙着准备食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经给朋友们发了请帖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘想逃跑，但是外面太冷了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我应该怎么做？”她自言自语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘，现在必须要走了。”格雷夫人抓住她的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去哪里？”拇指姑娘问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人的鼻子动了动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生想让你去新家看看。”她激动地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他邀请我们去喝茶。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当老鼠打开后门时，洛夫斯先生早已经在那里等候了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，洛夫斯先生！”格雷夫人惊讶地说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得过来接你们。”他嘟囔道，“有个小问题。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么问题？”老鼠惊讶地喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“通往我家的地道坏了，”洛夫斯先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会指给你们看的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身走进黑暗的地道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“带上灯，拇指姑娘。”格雷夫人说道，“紧紧跟着我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跟着洛夫斯先生走进了黑暗的地道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘只能看见前面格雷夫人的尾巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然拇指姑娘看到了前面的亮光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>前面的地道上有个洞通向外界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从洞里投进来一束光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只鸟躺在地道的地面上。它一动也不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了？”格雷夫人问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这只讨厌的鸟掉进了我们的地道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洛夫斯先生边说边用手杖戳那只鸟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那只鸟死了吗？”格雷夫人问道，“我们该怎么做？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘走上前去，用灯照亮那只鸟的身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”拇指姑娘大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是有点儿吓人，我知道。”洛夫斯先生亲切的说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，我已经处理了一切。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是鼹鼠并不知道真正吓到拇指姑娘的是什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸟的一条腿上绑着一条线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这只鸟就是拇指姑娘的朋友皮特。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经跟斯利姆说了。”洛夫斯先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他过几天会把鸟拖走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“斯利姆？那只狼？”格雷夫人说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼？”拇指姑娘问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“斯利姆会把尸体挪走的。”洛夫斯先生解释道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后我就可以修理地道了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘盯着死鸟看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可怜的朋友。”她小声说，然后开始哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没事吧，亲爱的？”格雷夫人问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我有事，”拇指姑娘大声喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转身朝格雷夫人房子的方向跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>